{"title":"历史的档案——下延安一个小煤矿断想","authors":["叶延滨"],"dates":[{"year":1985,"month":4,"day":15}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"历史的档案"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——下延安一个小煤矿断想"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叶延滨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真没有想到煤层"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这样地薄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两层石头夹层"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炭下井直不起腰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挖炭躺着刨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炭却亮锃锃的好"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一张破报纸能点着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也点着我的烦恼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个灼人的发现"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心里头烧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们向这块土地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"索取的太多太多了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地面种粮地里筑窑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地心里捣炭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"取了多少温饱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高原的历史，是母亲的档案袋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孕育一个民族的母亲啊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只写下两个字：给予"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"儿孙们看到没看到？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我惊恐而不安，扛起树苗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不安地在植树节把树浇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真怕浇不掉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历史写下的：不孝！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}